Subject: Re: [T2] Idle Issues

I would verify in this order.

No vacuum leaks.
Aux air valve, verify open when cold. The disc can stick intermittently.
Temp sensor readings, connections.
Idle switch.

If all that is good, verify base timing and idle mixture adjustment.

